VALUES
  ('optician-moex-00599', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何項檢查方法可用來評估患者的調節靈敏度（accommodativefacility）？', '["球面翻轉鏡法（flippers）", "負鏡片法（minuslenstoblur）", "推近法（push-up）", "拉遠法（pull-away）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00600', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者有+1.00D遠視眼，在未配戴矯正眼鏡下，以負鏡片法（minuslenstoblur）進行調節幅度測試。當 視標置於40cm處，逐漸加入負球面度直到-8.00D時，受檢者開始感到視標持續模糊，則該眼的調節幅度 為下列何者？', '["7D", "8D", "10.5D", "11.5D"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00601', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在測量近用加入度（nearADD）時，以負相對調節力（negativerelativeaccommodation,NRA）及正相對調 節力（positiverelativeaccommodation,PRA）對初始暫定加入度（initialtentativeADD）進行微調。若受檢 者首次持續看不清楚（firstsustainedblur）視標時，加入度為+2.00D以及+0.50D，而初始暫定加入度（initial tentativeADD）為+1.00D。下列何者正確？', '["NRA為+1.00D，PRA為-1.00D", "NRA為+1.50D，PRA為-0.50D", "最終暫定加入度（finaltentativeADD）+1.50D", "最終暫定加入度（finaltentativeADD）+1.25D"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00602', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '檢影鏡跟屈光檢查後顯示：雙眼+4.00DS，慣用眼鏡度數是+3.00DS，調節幅度是5.75D，透過慣用眼鏡 時的近點調節（nearpointofaccommodation）距離最接近多少？', '["10cm", "15cm", "20cm", "25cm"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00603', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關於雙眼平衡步驟，下列何者為正確的操作？', '["即使是60歲以上已然毫無調節力的病人，也應該進行平衡測試", "當使用單眼雲霧法（monocularfogging）時，雲霧度數越多越好", "執行漢弗萊斯立即對比法（Humphrissimmediatecontrast）時，正鏡片與負鏡片的測試時間都是各1秒鐘 為宜", "對於雙眼最佳矯正視力不等的患者可使用稜鏡分離紅綠測試（prism-dissociated duochrome test）進行雙 眼平衡"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00604', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知45歲正視眼（emmetropia）受檢者的調節幅度為3.5D，配戴著+0.75D 閱讀眼鏡。若不考慮焦深（depth offocus），則其最大清晰視覺範圍（rangeofclearvision）最接近下列何者？', '["15～80cm", "40～130cm", "25～130cm", "25～80cm"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00605', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者於 40 cm 進行融像性交叉柱鏡測試（fused cross cylinder），發現有 0.75 D 調節遲滯（lag of accommodation），則該距離的調節反應（accommodativeresponse）為何？', '["0.75D", "1.75D", "2.50D", "3.25D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00606', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者的遠點位於眼後2m，當其注視眼前50cm處電腦螢幕時，理論上須使用的調節力為下列何者？', '["0.50D", "1.00D", "2.00D", "2.50D"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00607', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者配戴-2.50D的眼鏡，以推進法（push-up）檢查得知調節近點（nearpointofaccommodation,NPA） 位於眼前8cm。若已知該眼實際的調節幅度為10D，則其原有的遠距屈光不正為下列何者？', '["近視-4.50D", "近視-5.00D", "近視-5.50D", "近視-6.00D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00608', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '眼睛要能持久近距離工作，一般應保留多少的調節幅度？', '["保留1/5的調節幅度", "保留1/4的調節幅度", "保留1/3的調節幅度", "保留1/2的調節幅度"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f682e76ad4b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ee9d4e54516d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL)
